data.description: Assumable Loan offered with this property or 2/1 rate buydown. Spacious home in Manchester Park of Lexington with 3604 sq ft of living space & an inviting backyard oasis, recently updated (2022) with a custom patio, beautiful landscaping, above ground pool & shed with electric. Offers 4 bedrooms, 3 FULL bathrooms, one of the bedrooms on the main floor adjacent to a full bathrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or guests. In addition, there is a loft & office with shelving, bay window & French doors, creating a perfect space for work or study. When you enter, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that flow seamlessly into the formal dining room & kitchen. Fully equipped eat in kitchen with granite countertops, tons of cabinets, Butler's pantry with more cabinets, a large pantry & island with bar seating which creates a perfect space for preparing meals & entertaining guests as it also opens up to a huge great room. Generous-sized master suite offers a sitting area, large his and her walk-in closets/en suite bathroom that includes dual vanity, a separate shower, a garden tub & water closet, providing a luxurious and private retreat within the home. Additional bedrooms upstairs, each with its own walk-in closet. Upstairs Loft area with a projector & movie screen, creating a fantastic entertainment space for movie nights & gaming. Less maintenance with ionizer system in pool, termite bond & gutter guards recently added (2023). Make this YOUR NEW HOME today!
